        <h3 class="p-optTitle__title" data-reveal-title>Leaflet Concepts with Distinct Creative Directions</h3>
        <p class="p-optTitle__body" data-reveal-body>Three design concepts were developed with different approaches to message emphasis and visual direction, based on the leaflet’s purpose and target audience. <br />Each concept varied in information layout and visual flow, allowing us to evaluate which direction was most effective for communicating the opening announcement and encouraging consultation inquiries.</p>
        <span class="p-optTitle__rule" aria-hidden="true" data-reveal-body></span>
